Who are you consuming in real life & on social media? Because it is most definitely consuming you (for better or worse). That includes YOURSELF! ✨🙌🏽

How’s your self-talk? 💗 How are you? Your heart, your head. It’s the beginning of a new month, a great time for a fresh start and a little check-in. Do you build yourself up, encourage, give grace, speak highly of yourself in your head? It matters. Confidence starts with the belief in yourself and that starts with your ability to keep the promises you make to yourself. 
Just a little reminder that you are a badass and you got this, whatever “this” is. 🤜🏽🤛🏽

Ok! Let’s talk air dried natural summaaaa hair ☀️ what are your ride or die products?👇🏽I want this post to be super helpful for everyone, so go to town in the comments and save to reference back! 👯‍♀️

Big Sephora bag of all hair products I’m testing and your top recks I picked up today. Specially for air delaying curly/wavy hair (& less frizz!) in the summer & really year round 🐬🦀🌊

Also, tip for non curly girls who want the look - apply product, braid + take them out when they are almost dry! 

+ Oribe Matte Wave Texture Lotion 
+ Kristen Ess Air Dry Cream
+ WOW Dream Coat Supernatural Spray
+ OUAI Wave Spray
+ Briogeo Don’t Despair Repair
+ Kerastase Curl Manifest Line - Shampoo & Conditioner, Leave in Treatment 
+ VERB curl cream 
+ Moroccan Oil Curl Defining Cream
+ Moroccan Oil Intense Curl Cream
